        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Allophoma thunbergiae (GUCC 2070.7) a. Leaf symptoms on the host; b, c. Pycnidia forming on PDA; d, e. Colony on PDA (front and reverse); f, g. Colony on MEA (front and reverse); h, i. Colony on OA (front and reverse); j, k. Section of pycnidium; l. Section of pycnidial wall; m, n. Conidiogenous cells; o. Conidia. Scale bars: b, c = 500 μm; j = 100 μm; k = 50 μm; l = 20 μm; m-o = 5 μm." ;
